\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Project Name:
\f1\b0  My Comms Coach\

\f0\b Target Persona:
\f1\b0  Non-native English speaker working as a 
\f0\b Quality Assurance (QA) Officer
\f1\b0  in a Sydney-based furniture e-commerce business.\

\f0\b Problem:
\f1\b0  The user needs to communicate technical quality issues (e.g., fabric durability, furniture assembly defects, shipping damage) to internal cross-functional teams like finance & customer care, local warehouse teams and international suppliers, while also mastering "Sydney workplace chitchat" to build rapport with internal teams. \

\f0\b Tech Stack Requirements:
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Frontend:
\f1\b0  Flutter 4.0. Needs a clean "Inspection Room" UI with a real-time waveform and a "Correction Overlay" that displays text-based feedback while the audio is live.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Backend:
\f1\b0  Python + 
\f0\b LiveKit Agents
\f1\b0 . This is the WebRTC bridge for sub-300ms latency.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 AI Brain:
\f1\b0  gemini-3.1-flash-live-preview. Use the A2A (Audio-to-Audio) pipeline.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Orchestration:
\f1\b0  
\f0\b OpenClaw
\f1\b0 . Use OpenClaw to manage session state. Before a voice session starts, the app must call an OpenClaw "Skill" to fetch the "Daily QA Scenario."\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

