\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Topic Selection:
\f1\b0  Choose from: 'Reporting a broken dining table shipment,' 'Explaining a complex assembly instruction to a customer,' or 'Small talk with the truck drivers at the loading dock.'\
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Difficulty Setting:
\f1\b0  Check the local user_progress.db. If the user has completed 5 sessions, set the scenario to 'High-Stakes Dispute with a Supplier over Fabric Quality.'\
\ls4\ilvl0
